101
00:06:47.083 --> 00:06:48.917
Thank you. CEO Kang.

102
00:06:49.083 --> 00:06:51.583
Please give him a round of applause!

103
00:06:59.083 --> 00:07:01.500
Next. to introduce Chains Bio's global market strategy 000

104
