298
00:20:33.167 --> 00:20:34.583
What the hell?

299
00:21:00.667 --> 00:21:01.667
What the fuck?

300
00:21:23.917 --> 00:21:25.083
What the hell is this?

301
00:21:55.167 --> 00:21:57.333
